psalm.text:
[[Ps 18,31]]God's way is unerring; 
the LORD'S promise is tried and true; 
he is a shield for all who trust in him.

[[Ps 18,47]]The LORD lives! And blessed be my rock! 
Extolled be God my savior.
[[Ps 18,50]]Thus I will proclaim you, LORD, among the nations;
I will sing the praises of your name.

[[Ps 18,51]]You who gave great victories to your king 
And showed kindness to your anointed;
to David and his posterity forever.
